snippet.title: Waste Land Waste Disposal Winter Games Expo Trailer
snippet.description:
Winter Games Expo Trailer. 
Wasteland Waste Disposal is an Indiegame where you 
♻️Recycle, Refine, and Rebuild the apocalyptic wasteland
🚜Explore a small open-world with a mech fortress
👥Onboard survivors, and build settlements 
#wintergamesexpo
Sountrack by Brian Wilson
